data.description: Must see 5 BR/4.5 BA beautifully updated home with a stunningly serene setting. Large entry w/ formal living room & sep. family room. Gleaming, real hrdwd floors, incredible hand-crafted crown molding & wainscoting, w/ 2 fireplaces! This spacious floorplan boasts a chef's kitchen which incl. a KitchenAid commercial 6-burner stove w/ double oven, SS vent hood & appliances surrounding an expansive island. This incredibly equipped and large kitchen is sure to inspire anyone! Formal DR. 1st floor, expansive Owner's Retreat includes an ensuite with an oversized jetted tub, full shwr, dbl sinks, walk-in closet & private terrace. Original hardwoods and landing upstairs with four graciously proportioned bedrooms. Two BRs share a jack & jill bath. Two larger BR's at either end of the hallway have vaulted ceilings and can be utilized as a secondary MB or additional family living areas. One being used as an artist's studio currently. Large basement w/ rec room, wet bar & full bath. Relax on the 14'x18' screened-in patio overlooking the serenity of the surrounding towering trees & landscaping, which opens up to paver/stone patios & a cozy fire pit surrounded by towering trees. Plenty of storage in the multiple 'walk-in' attic spaces for your seasonal decor; or finish them into extra living areas. Fresh Ext. Paint! This is the perfect blend of spacious & cozy. Don't miss out on this charming home!
